DOC.brief_summary: Urodynamic study objective method evaluate female patient low urinary tract symptom ( LUTS ) . However , method include place urinary catheter , thus prevents routine method evaluate follow patient LUTS . Therefore , necessary find simple objective method help evaluate female patient LUTS . Several kind biomarker report diagnosing patient overactive bladder ; however , sensitivity remain poor . The aim study find useful biomarker , biomarkers , combination , aid urodynamic study , objectively precisely evaluate female patient LUTS .
DOC.brief_title: Studies Biomarkers Different Urodynamic Diagnoses Female Patients With Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms
DOC.criteria: All female patient ( > 20 year ) Lower urinary tract syndrome . Female patient tumor stone exclude .
